        "text": "The entire discipline of graphic design, which PLT mostly ignores, is concerned with visual properties applicable to text. I only know of two papers that try to codify those aspects in a programming context:\n<https:\/\/hal.inria.fr\/hal-00737414>\n<https:\/\/dl.acm.org\/citation.cfm?id=2661138>",
